Our Latest Results vs. Baselines

HTML generated at: 2024-09-24 22:32:04

Legend

Ground Truth

GT instance segmentation from SketchyScene 7k dataset

Real Image & Voting Pipeline

Given a sketch, we caption, generate real images, and run grounded SAM on the real images. We then cluster the masks from all seeds' results.

Experiment: Expanded Caption

We ask LlaVa to generate detailed caption of all objects in the sketch.

Experiment: Iterative Segmentation

Up to 4 iterations, we repeat the real image & voting pipeline on left over non-segmeneted sketch pixels until entire sketch has been segmented.

Grounded SAM on Sketch

Directly running Grounded SAM on the sketches.

Experiment: Naive SAM

We run regular Segment Anything instead of grounded SAM.
